{"route":"/docs/reference/data-loading/read/","title":"Read","description":"Documentation for the `read` function.","part":null,"outline":[{"id":"summary","name":"概要","children":[]},{"id":"例","name":"例","children":[]},{"id":"parameters","name":"引数","children":[{"id":"parameters-path","name":"path","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-encoding","name":"encoding","children":[]}]}],"body":{"kind":"func","content":{"path":[],"name":"read","title":"Read","keywords":[],"oneliner":"ファイルからプレーンテキストやデータを読み込む。","element":false,"contextual":false,"deprecation":null,"details":"<p>ファイルからプレーンテキストやデータを読み込む。</p>\n<p>デフォルトでは、ファイルはUTF-8として読み込まれ、<a href=\"/docs/reference/foundations/str/\">文字列</a>として返されます。</p>\n<p><code>encoding: <span class=\"typ-key\">none</span></code>を指定した場合、この関数は代わりに生の<a href=\"/docs/reference/foundations/bytes/\" title=\"bytes\">bytes</a>を返します。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例\">例</h2>\n<div class=\"previewed-code\"><pre><code>An example for a HTML file: <span class=\"typ-escape\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"typ-key\">#</span><span class=\"typ-key\">let</span> text <span class=\"typ-op\">=</span> <span class=\"typ-func\">read</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;example.html&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n<span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">raw</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>text<span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span> lang<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;html&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n\nRaw bytes:\n<span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">read</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;tiger.jpg&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span> encoding<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-key\">none</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n</code></pre><div class=\"preview\"><img src=\"/docs/assets/b92e43ad9c335363c8a8efef74973b19.png\" alt=\"Preview\"></div></div>","example":null,"self":false,"params":[{"name":"path","details":"<p>ファイルのパス。</p>\n<p>詳細については、<a href=\"/docs/reference/syntax/#paths\">パスのセクション</a>を参照してください。</p>","example":null,"types":["str"],"strings":[],"default":null,"positional":true,"named":false,"required":true,"variadic":false,"settable":false},{"name":"encoding","details":"<p>ファイルを読み込む際に使用するエンコーディング。</p>\n<p><code><span class=\"typ-key\">none</span></code>に設定すると、この関数は生のバイトを返します。</p>","example":null,"types":["none","str"],"strings":[{"string":"utf8","details":"<p>Unicode UTF-8エンコーディング。</p>"}],"default":"<code><span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;utf8&quot;</span></code>","positional":false,"named":true,"required":false,"variadic":false,"settable":false}],"returns":["str","bytes"],"scope":[]}}}